{
  "stem": "18626.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'll tell you the thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "When they [GERMAN] were closed, a German gestapo truck came in to pick up some laundry in the-- because it was a laundry department.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And nobody was there in the [GERMAN] no more.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Everybody was already gone, you know, to the transport, to the railroad-- to the railroad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I was still there with my family in the [GERMAN] yard, because in the [GERMAN] yard was a [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "A [YIDDISH] means there was a cellar dug out by some people who walked in the [GERMAN] during the years, a hiding place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And one of the Jewish police who were all the time in the [GERMAN] gate staying all the time was a very good friend of my Uncle Boris.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he told me-- his name was Yonkel Glick, Jacob Glick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He says, Maishke.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Your mother is here, and children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Let's go underneath.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There's a [YIDDISH], a bunker in the ground with a certain hiding place to hide.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we'll go under there, and maybe we'll wait out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The Russians, the Soviet army, is not far from Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "In weeks, Lithuania is going to be liberated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So we crawled in in that with my family, my mother and my brother and sister, inside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But other people maybe knew about that bunker too, and life is very dear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Everybody wants to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So more people with force, I want to go in too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to be alive too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So everybody start to press himself in in that bunker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In that [YIDDISH], called in Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The [YIDDISH] was not big enough to take so many people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother and even me, we start to feel like we are going to faint there.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
